Prophet Paseka "Mboro" Motsoeneng's Incredible Happenings church in Katlehong on the East Rand will resemble a storeroom of panties on Sunday next week. This after Mboro asked women with sexual dysfunctions to bring their lingerie to him to pray for them so they could get their coital appetite back. Today, about 100 women who complained of sexual dysfunctions will also bring their sanitary pads to Mboro for prayers. TO READ THE FULL STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD AT YOUR NEAREST STORE